          "metadata": {
            "curation_policy": "<ol>\n<li>If an uploaded document has an existing DOI, it will be kept. If there is no DOI, a Zenodo DOI will be minted for the item.</li>\n<li>Items with Open Access remain Open Access.</li>\n<li>Items with closed access remain closed. If they are published on 31.12.1999 or earlier, they are made accessible for reading. Please consult your national copyright law for conditions of reuse.</li>\n<li>To upload publications, please contact <a href=\"mailto:info@plazi.org\">info@plazi.org</a>.</li>\n</ol>",
